tion_allowances]]</td></tr><tr><td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px">ACCOMMODATION</td><td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px">[[housing_allowance]]</td></tr><tr><td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px">TRANSPORTATION</td><td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px">[[transportation_allowance]]</td></tr><tr><td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px">OTHER ALLOWANCE</td><td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px">[[other_allowance]]</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px">[[salary_allowances]]</td><td style="border: 1px solid black; padding: 5px"><span style="font-weight: bold">Unpaid Leave Deduction</span>&nbsp;<span style="font-family: Segoe-UI; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">[[attendance_deduction]],</span></td></tr></tbody></table><div class="totals" style="margin-top: 10px"><strong>TOTAL EARNINGS:</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>[[total_earning]]<br /><strong>TOTAL DEDUCTIONS:</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>-<span>&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Segoe-UI; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">[[total_deduction_with_attendance]]</span><br /><strong>NET PAY:</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>[[net_amount]]</div><div class="signature" style="margin-top: 30px">RECEIVED DATE: ___________________________<br /><br />SIGNATURE: _______________________________</div></div><div style="text-align: center">[[footer]],</div><p><br style=" font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px" /></p><br /></p>